The fact that West opened doesn't change your hand at all. You had planned on <b>Opening</b> 3\S, now you make a <b>Weak Jump Overcall</b> of 3\S. If partner has some "stuff" you might get to a makeable contract, and if he doesn't you may keep the opponents out of a \H game.

This time everybody passes.}

